*** ENGLISH ***

Chaos: Wizard War II is a mythical strategy board game for 1 to 8
players.

NEW FOR v3.4cd:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
* The digital sound effects weren't working when playing the game direct
  from a cover CD.  Oops.  This is now fixed.

* Several features were requested by Chaos players from around the world
  and I added them in.

* Many very rare bugs/flaws were fixed.  None of these bugs crashed the
  machine, they were just "technically incorrect" and usually quite funny
  but they were so rare and involved such weird spell combos that a normal
  person could play the game for a whole year and not find them.

* Some improved AI.


NEW FEATURES for v3.3!
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
* Exploration!  For years this was only available to registered users but
  now it is available in the Aminet version!  Feel the fear as you explore
  each new square!  Tremble in Terror as you hear the roars and screams of
  hideous monsters without knowing if you will be their next meal!

* Blood! Creatures now bleed when wounded!  And you can rip their legs off
  }:>  This is only available for creatures which have had bloody versions
  drawn: Lion, Leopard and Elephant are the only ones so far.  Send in your
  bloody creations for inclusion in the next version.  Leave the Blood
  option off when playing with small children or risk psychological trauma.
  :)

* Dungeon Wars!  Turn this on and a random dungeon will be generated for
  you to explore and fight in.  Can you survive in the dungeons of death?

* Ruthlessness!  Turn this on and computer players will fight in a more
  ruthless and intelligent manner.  If you turn this off they will attack
  in a more or less random manner.

* MANY more improvements too numerous to mention!  If you really want to
  know about all the new stuff then you'll hafta read the history file. :)

